  "summary": {
    "as": "Introduced in House",
    "asOf": "2022-06-23",
    "date": "2023-08-23T14:22:53Z",
    "text": "Supporting Opportunities to Build Everyday Responsibility Act of 2022 or the SOBER Act of 2022\n\nThis bill directs the Department of Justice to establish a grant program to provide funding for 24-7 sobriety programs. It also directs the National Institute of Justice to evaluate the policies and procedures used by grant recipients to reduce crime, recidivism, and incarceration attributed to use of alcohol or controlled substances."
